  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will construct an Inclusive Index of Prosperity (IPI) to assess Scotland&apos;s prosperity.Through this project, we aim to show that, by creating an index that is complementary to GDP, it is possible to present a more comprehensive picture of the prosperity of a country.   This proposal is unique in that public participation in determining the composition of the Index will be central to the process.</narrative>
